				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$=\,$$\end{document}2.06 mV) for channels with the lowest electronic noise. At the start of science run 0 the SPE acceptance was around 89% increasing to 93% after optimization of the thresholds.

